{"tid":959712,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然好多人都話靚仔或身型好嘅人求其著都得，但佢地未必係咁諗。","createTime":"2018-12-28T20:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T06:13:32.000Z","uid":227650,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d50e757fb9a3dbcc75355bfebf1552c45c9147","tid":959712,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:56:20.000Z","msg":"現實生活中，我都識幾個靚仔或身型好(或者兩者皆備)嘅人，佢地衣著一啲都唔hea，反而成日聽到佢地問人「 我咁著好唔好睇？」「會唔會有啲更好嘅襯法？」呢兩句證明佢地對自己好有要求、對衣著嘅態度都好有要求。<br />\n<br />\n雖然靚仔著咩都好睇呢個講法係啱，但係都可以喺另一面睇，善用天生麗質去做得更好;對自己更有要求㗎嘛。<br />\n<br />\n以下呢個人應該無人會否認佢係靚仔同埋身型好呱？但佢一樣好著重衣著，甚至小小細節都唔放過。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/045451_a2ac83e1f6d9042c93cc6dd1ec263e5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F29%2F045451_a2ac83e1f6d9042c93cc6dd1ec263e5d.jpg&h=5599acc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/045453_ce09ba47f2ebbb8d0176c72cdf908b6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F29%2F045453_ce09ba47f2ebbb8d0176c72cdf908b6f.jpg&h=52a58f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/045456_712fb6bd2259d9f65cc90e5902fea606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F29%2F045456_712fb6bd2259d9f65cc90e5902fea606.jpg&h=c2d162e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"887a72346a02c79f2392f8f0729f6f3d57f292e8","tid":959712,"uid":54923,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T21:22:06.000Z","msg":"講緊係求其啦 事實上日日搽野洗臉敷masks 對自己好多要求"},{"pid":"bc0e220e32fa578e0965eab636eaf1c463354ed6","tid":959712,"uid":227650,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"887a72346a02c79f2392f8f0729f6f3d57f292e8","tid":959712,"uid":54923,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T21:22:06.000Z","msg":"講緊係求其啦 事實上日日搽野洗臉敷masks 對自己好多要求"},"citedB